Contract locking ether found in /unique_chucks/35/0xe3cc697219a23cdc24df5a3b7f35497b8f3f153a.sol:
	Contract KATMTokenChanger has payable functions:
	 - fallback (/unique_chucks/35/0xe3cc697219a23cdc24df5a3b7f35497b8f3f153a.sol)
	But does not have a function to withdraw the ether

TokenRetriever.retrieveTokens (/unique_chucks/35/0xe3cc697219a23cdc24df5a3b7f35497b8f3f153a.sol#358-371) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-tokenInstance.transfer(msg.sender,tokenBalance) (/unique_chucks/35/0xe3cc697219a23cdc24df5a3b7f35497b8f3f153a.sol#369-370)
